In re Resignation of Hall.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Hall (1990), 53 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. 90-1202 Submitted July 19, 1990 Decided July 25, 1990.)

The resignation of Charles H. Hall as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
